{"has_more_entries": true, "subscriptions": "", "error": "", "posts": [{"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsnK7JhJ", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 469, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8669331, "raw_content": "", "author": "goodguy", "created": 1781003053075, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "AcAirman", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsnK7JhJ.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/INw19EaCkdfF.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/K9e2UpDQm94FBQMu.jpeg", "width": 768, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 552}], "blurhash": "U7I=DYE18|f802WAr?WX_Nt7s,Rj00ozS7n~", "full_resolution": [575, 800]}, "title": "I'm Sick of this Shit", "last_comment_created": 1781016733847, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 4, "score_up": 469, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsrqaNeb", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 46, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8670861, "raw_content": "", "author": "FuckAllDemocrats", "created": 1781048425506, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsrqaNeb.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/J5MGddSCNvP1.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/G6wiQ3FXo3WKxY4H.jpeg", "width": 615, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "UWLX*[kXysWC00ogTLax.9n$n%oe-:WBrqof", "full_resolution": [1332, 1066]}, "title": "Carmelo regrets not converting to Islam so he can knife people to death freely in UK", "last_comment_created": 1781048425504, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 0, "score_up": 46, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsrrgZz4", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 35, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8671096, "raw_content": "**I get it. A year and a half in, no arrests, \"2 weeks,\" the swamp looks as healthy as ever.** Easy to think nothing changes. But the Pulte appointment to Acting DNI has real potential, and the Democrats\u2019 reaction proves it.\n\n\n\n\nPulte isn\u2019t a career government employee. He\u2019s a **financial forensic specialist** who made his name understanding how money flows through complex systems, spotting fraud in places others miss. He\u2019s heading the Federal Housing Finance Agency and now the intelligence community simultaneously. That\u2019s not a coincidence. That\u2019s a man with a map and a flashlight dropped at the intersection of mortgage data and black budgets. **He knows how to follow the money.**\n\n\n\nIt's no secret that intelligence dark money gets laundered through the mortgage market, trillions in volume making billions disappear. Pulte understands structured finance at a level that most oversight never touches. He can spot the irregularity in a securitization, the shell company that doesn\u2019t add up, the property portfolio that screams \u201ccutout\u201d not \u201cinvestment.\u201d\n\n\n\n\nThe Democrats just threatened to let FISA 702 expire rather than let him look. They\u2019ve defended that program for years. Now, overnight, it\u2019s expendable? That\u2019s not a policy dispute, that\u2019s a hostage negotiation. They fear Pulte. Ask yourself why.\n\n---------------------\n\n\n**What It Would Take**\n\n\nHe needs outside forensic auditors, people not tainted by the intelligence community. He needs the authority to declassify and release findings. And he needs time, which is the one thing the deep state will try to deny him.\n\n---------------------\n\n\n**What He Doesn\u2019t Need to Do**\n\n\nHe doesn\u2019t have to uncover everything. He just has to crack the door open wide enough that others can peek inside and start pulling threads. One documented case of mortgage fraud tied to intelligence funding. One paper trail that proves the mechanism. That\u2019s all it takes for real journalists (yes, some still exist) and future investigators to go further.\nThe deep state\u2019s power isn\u2019t that it\u2019s invulnerable. It\u2019s what everyone believes it is. Pulte has the potential to unveil the swamp.", "author": "I-am-Orlando", "created": 1781054342130, "profile_picture": "TEnkk5XkT6JN", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "EvJohn", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Why Pulte Might Actually Matter (And Why the Dems Are Panicking)", "last_comment_created": 1781059735131, "content": "<p><strong>I get it. A year and a half in, no arrests, &quot;2 weeks,&quot; the swamp looks as healthy as ever.</strong> Easy to think nothing changes. But the Pulte appointment to Acting DNI has real potential, and the Democrats\u2019 reaction proves it.</p>\n<p>Pulte isn\u2019t a career government employee. He\u2019s a <strong>financial forensic specialist</strong> who made his name understanding how money flows through complex systems, spotting fraud in places others miss. He\u2019s heading the Federal Housing Finance Agency and now the intelligence community simultaneously. That\u2019s not a coincidence. That\u2019s a man with a map and a flashlight dropped at the intersection of mortgage data and black budgets. <strong>He knows how to follow the money.</strong></p>\n<p>It's no secret that intelligence dark money gets laundered through the mortgage market, trillions in volume making billions disappear. Pulte understands structured finance at a level that most oversight never touches. He can spot the irregularity in a securitization, the shell company that doesn\u2019t add up, the property portfolio that screams \u201ccutout\u201d not \u201cinvestment.\u201d</p>\n<p>The Democrats just threatened to let FISA 702 expire rather than let him look. They\u2019ve defended that program for years. Now, overnight, it\u2019s expendable? That\u2019s not a policy dispute, that\u2019s a hostage negotiation. They fear Pulte. Ask yourself why.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>What It Would Take</strong></p>\n<p>He needs outside forensic auditors, people not tainted by the intelligence community. He needs the authority to declassify and release findings. And he needs time, which is the one thing the deep state will try to deny him.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>What He Doesn\u2019t Need to Do</strong></p>\n<p>He doesn\u2019t have to uncover everything. He just has to crack the door open wide enough that others can peek inside and start pulling threads. One documented case of mortgage fraud tied to intelligence funding. One paper trail that proves the mechanism. That\u2019s all it takes for real journalists (yes, some still exist) and future investigators to go further.\nThe deep state\u2019s power isn\u2019t that it\u2019s invulnerable. It\u2019s what everyone believes it is. Pulte has the potential to unveil the swamp.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 2, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 35, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2064436942155231524", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsrqaeIq", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 43, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8670900, "raw_content": "", "author": "FuckAllDemocrats", "created": 1781049615394, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "sr20106", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsrqaeIq.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/freckledliberty/status/2064436942155231524?s=46&t=eC-6bvibHP_gKJ9ZlbrhfA", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "They are demon possessed, Satan owned", "last_comment_created": 1781061848897, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 20, "score_up": 43, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 1352, "created": 1781035097000, "id": "2064436942155231524", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2064436266524127232/img/-ljfAt3aAiscmG_Q.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video